QuestData.Title: A Taste for Grouper
QuestData.Description: Between boat rides and building, I'm exhausted... and hungry. You know what sounds tasty? Fish. Fish sound delicious.$B$BDarkshore is known for its grouper. If you fish me up some, I'll make it worth your time.
QuestData.LogDescription: Use your fishing skill to obtain 4 Darkshore Grouper.
